WEBVTT

00:00:59.583 --> 00:01:01.476
the bird migration,

00:01:01.500 --> 00:01:03.434
the size of fruits,

00:01:03.458 --> 00:01:05.268
the plant flowers.

00:01:05.292 --> 00:01:11.000
She can tell you by observing
the behavior of her own cattle.

00:01:11.833 --> 00:01:16.393
That's how she knows better
the weather and the ecosystem

00:01:16.417 --> 00:01:18.042
that she's living in.

00:01:19.208 --> 00:01:23.518
I'm coming from a pastoralist community

00:01:23.542 --> 00:01:25.351
who are cattle herders.

00:01:25.375 --> 00:01:27.434
We are nomadic.

00:01:27.458 --> 00:01:30.268
We move from one place to another one